          "title": "Saturday",
          "text": "<b><i class='far fa-clock'></i> 09:30 ~ 16:00 - Guided tour Rosia Montana.</b><br> Will start with the roman galleries from the Mining Museum and then will discover the goldsmiths stories and legends by visiting the patrimony buildings form the historical center of Rosia Montana (schools, churches or the goldsmith houses built by various civilizations who came here since antiquity to find gold, the reason why the area was proposed as UNESCO site).",
