          "text": "<br><br><b><i class='far fa-clock'></i> Evening - Movie screenings</b> <br>We will watch some movies made in the '70s in Rosia Montana like 'Nunta de piatra' (is in top 10 romanian movies of all times) or 'Flăcări pe Comori'."
