          "title": "Monday 30 April",
          "text": "<b><i class='far fa-clock'></i> 09:30 ~ 16:00 - Guided trail - Detunata massif</b>. <br>This 80m high massive formed from basalt columns is a protected area with huge stone blocks. The area has great legends, the people are welcoming and they also make some amazing cheese pies.",
