          "title": "Tuesday 1 Mai",
          "text": "<b>Steam train rides</b> <br>The <b>steamtrain</b> was used in the past to carry miners and gold from Gura Rosie factory and now has been open for tourists. There are 2 steamtrains near us: <b>Abrud - Câmpeni steamtrain</b> (~10min by car from us; the tour last 3h) and <b>Crișcior - Brad steamtrain</b> (~45min by car from us; the tour last 2h). <br><i class='fa fa-map-signs'></i> <b>How to get there?</b> - ",
